  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK940">
<l>iḻattoṟūuṅ kātalikkuñ cūtēpōl tuṉpa</l>
<l> muḻattoṟūuṅ kātaṟ ṟuyir</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As the gambler loves (his vice) the more he loses by it, so does the soul love (the body) the more it suffers through it.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
